(11, 'Professores de Tocantínia participam de cursos promovidos pela Universidade Federal do Tocantins', 'admin', '2021-03-24', 0, 'Publicada', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Por&nbsp;Leontina Martins<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />A pandemia do novo coronav&iacute;rus trouxe um grande desafio aos professores da Rede Municipal de Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o de Tocant&iacute;nia que tiveram&nbsp; &nbsp;que se adaptar junto &agrave;s ferramentas tecnol&oacute;gicas para melhor auxiliar os alunos durante o ensino remoto, tendo-se sempre a preocupa&ccedil;&atilde;o de garantir a qualidade da Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">O professor Andr&eacute; Goveia, titular&nbsp; &nbsp;Secretaria Municipal de Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o de Tocant&iacute;nia (SEMED), informou que a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o Municipal est&aacute; atenta a essa realidade, por isso, ao longo desse per&iacute;odo de pandemia, tem viabilizado um leque de cursos estrat&eacute;gicos &nbsp;que fazem parte da forma&ccedil;&atilde;o continuada dos professores do munic&iacute;pio.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Andr&eacute; Goveia&nbsp; afirmou que 2020 n&atilde;o foi um ano f&aacute;cil, pois&nbsp; a Covid-19 e a &nbsp;suspens&atilde;o das aulas presenciais&nbsp; que&nbsp; levou &agrave; &nbsp;mudan&ccedil;a no formato de atendimento, &nbsp;trouxeram desafios extras para a Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o, especialmente para os alunos mais vulner&aacute;veis.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&ldquo;Como forma de garantir uma Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o de qualidade para todos em Tocant&iacute;nia, a SEMED&nbsp; &nbsp;tem estimulado a&nbsp; participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos&nbsp; professores das nossas escolas municipais nas diversas etapas da forma&ccedil;&atilde;o continuada, buscando &nbsp;&nbsp;fortalecer seus conhecimentos, habilidades e compet&ecirc;ncias digitais e presenciais com pr&aacute;ticas inovadoras de ensino e aprendizagem para ambientes virtuais, de ensino h&iacute;brido e volta &agrave;s aulas&rdquo;, explicou Goveia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Na ter&ccedil;a-feira (23), por exemplo, os professores&nbsp;&nbsp; da Rede Municipal de Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o de Tocant&iacute;nia participaram, via&nbsp; Plataforma Google Meet, &nbsp;da &nbsp;Maratona de Minicursos de Teatro Online, numa parceria com a Universidade Federal do Tocantins (UFT).&nbsp; Outros cursos que os professores de Tocant&iacute;nia tamb&eacute;m participaram foram o de&nbsp; Teatro Popular, com M&ocirc;nica Raiane, Musicaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o e Cantigas Populares, com Bianca Melo e Luan Crispim, al&eacute;m de Jogos Teatrais, com Juliana Maia e&nbsp; Vin&iacute;cius de Oliveira, do curso de&nbsp; Licenciatura em Teatro da UFT.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #373a3c;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0345bf; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; transition: color 400ms ease 0s, background-color 400ms ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.n1to.com.br/noticia/4871/professores-de-tocantinia-participam-de-cursos-promovidos-pela-universidade-federal-do-tocantins\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.n1to.com.br/noticia/4871/professores-de-tocantinia-participam-de-cursos-promovidos-pela-universidade-federal-do-tocantins&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1616692294838000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGL6DiNOTdRpz8mMfbLhX_bK5Labw\">Fonte: Leontina Martins - Portal Not&iacute;cia 1</a></span></span></p>', 1, '2021-05-05 15:08:06', '2021-05-05 15:08:06', NULL, 'professores-de-tocantinia-participam-de-cursos-promovidos-pela-universidade-federal-do-tocantins-24-03-2021'),
(16, 'Secretário de Educação de Tocantínia emite comunicado sobre o caderno de atividades dos alunos do município', 'admin', '2021-03-10', 0, 'Publicada', '<div class=\"body-wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; transition: all 0.6s ease 0s; backface-visibility: hidden; right: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"body-innerwrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-x: hidden;\">\r\n<section id=\"sp-main-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 65px 0px 100px;\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 1140px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 1140px;\">\r\n<div class=\"container-inner\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><main id=\"sp-component\" class=\"col-lg-12 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%;\" role=\"main\">\r\n<div class=\"sp-column \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"article-details \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div id=\"sp-page-builder\" class=\"sp-page-builder sppb-article-page-wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative;\">\r\n<div class=\"page-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<section id=\"section-id-1615406489484\" class=\"sppb-section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; z-index: 1; position: relative; will-change: top; padding: 50px 0px; margin: 0px; box-shadow: #ffffff 0px 0px 0px 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-row-container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; z-index: 3; width: 1110px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; max-width: 1140px;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-row\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\">\r\n<div id=\"column-wrap-id-1615406489483\" class=\"sppb-col-md-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1110px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%;\">\r\n<div id=\"column-id-1615406489483\" class=\"sppb-column\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 1080px; height: 1113.26px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; box-shadow: #ffffff 0px 0px 0px 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-column-addons\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 1080px;\">\r\n<div id=\"sppb-addon-wrapper-1615406489487\" class=\"sppb-addon-wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 30px;\">\r\n<div id=\"sppb-addon-1615406489487\" class=\"clearfix \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; box-shadow: #ffffff 0px 0px 0px 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-addon sppb-addon-text-block  \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-addon-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">O secret&aacute;rio Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o de Tocant&iacute;nia, Andr&eacute; Goveia, divulgou nesta ter&ccedil;a-feira (9), um comunicado aos pais de alunos, alunos e tamb&eacute;m, a todos os servidores da Rede Municipal de Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o que nesta semana n&atilde;o ser&aacute; entregue o caderno com o bloco de atividades quinzenais, devido as medidas que a administra&ccedil;&atilde;o municipal est&aacute; tomando visando prevenir a prolifera&ccedil;&atilde;o da Covid-19 no munic&iacute;pio, conforme decreto do Poder Executivo Municipal.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n<div id=\"porta-316753037\" class=\"porta-2-dentro-do-texto\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0345bf; text-decoration-line: none; transition: color 400ms ease 0s, background-color 400ms ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IGkuoQnDsmE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://portaldoamaral.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GurupiCamCovid.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" srcset=\"https://portaldoamaral.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GurupiCamCovid.jpg 620w, https://portaldoamaral.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/GurupiCamCovid-560x226.jpg 560w\" alt=\"\" width=\"509\" height=\"191\" /></a></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Por conta disso, a Secretaria Municipal de Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o de Tocant&iacute;nia orienta pais e alunos para que procurem revisar os cadernos do bloco anterior at&eacute; o dia 17 de mar&ccedil;o, data que&nbsp;&nbsp; se finda os feitos do decreto, ocasi&atilde;o quando a partir de ent&atilde;o, come&ccedil;ar&aacute; a ser entregue o pr&oacute;ximo caderno de atividades.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Confira o comunicado do secret&aacute;rio:</em></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"sppb-addon-wrapper-1615406489490\" class=\"sppb-addon-wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 30px;\">\r\n<div id=\"sppb-addon-1615406489490\" class=\"clearfix \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; box-shadow: #ffffff 0px 0px 0px 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-addon sppb-addon-video \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"sppb-addon-video-local-video-wrap\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-top: 608.031px; position: relative;\"><video class=\"sppb-addon-video-local-source\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; height: 608.031px; width: 1080p