olor Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">desmatamento, pois tanto o ser humano, os animais e as plantas necessitam da &aacute;gua para</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">sobreviv&ecirc;ncia. Segundo a Marina Carvalho, existe uma necessidade de atua&ccedil;&atilde;o mais</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">efetiva no que se refere aos recursos h&iacute;dricos, em termos de investimentos, pol&iacute;ticas</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">p&uacute;blicas e ed